1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,336
KAI: I'm telling you, ZARA, this case is going cold. We've got nothing but dead ends.

2
00:00:06,336 --> 00:00:12,240
ZARA: That's not true, Kai. We've got a lead on the nightclub owner, Ryker.

3
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:17,208
KAI: Ryker's been in the system for years. He's not our guy.

4
00:00:17,208 --> 00:00:23,160
ZARA: Maybe not, but he's got connections to the underground. We need to dig deeper.

5
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:29,472
KAI: I'll take the lead on Ryker. You work on tracking down the source of the encrypted files.

6
00:00:29,472 --> 00:00:33,288
ZARA: I'm on it. I'll have something by morning.

7
00:00:33,288 --> 00:00:35,808
KAI: Ryker, we need to talk.

8
00:00:35,808 --> 00:00:38,544
RYKER: Ah, Detective Kai. What can I do for you?

9
00:00:38,544 --> 00:00:44,232
KAI: I'm investigating a string of cybercrimes. I hear you're involved.

10
00:00:44,232 --> 00:00:50,040
RYKER: Cybercrimes? Me? I'm a businessman, Detective. I don't get involved in that sort of thing.

11
00:00:50,040 --> 00:00:57,840
KAI: Save it, Ryker. I know all about your connections to the underground. You're hiding something.

12
00:00:57,840 --> 00:01:04,872
RYKER: I'm not hiding anything, Detective. But I'll make you a deal. If you can find what you're looking for, I'll give you a piece of the action.

13
00:01:04,872 --> 00:01:12,096
KAI: I think I found the source of the encrypted files. It's a private server, hidden deep in the underground.

14
00:01:12,096 --> 00:01:17,112
ZARA: Get us access to the server. We need to dig through the files.

15
00:01:17,112 --> 00:01:24,864
KAI: Already on it. But I've got a bad feeling about this, Zara. Ryker's not what he seems.

16
00:01:24,864 --> 00:01:34,632
ZARA: I know. I've been digging into his past. He's got a lot of connections to the shadow net. We're dealing with something big.

17
00:01:34,632 --> 00:01:38,256
KAI: Let's gear up. We're going in.

18
00:01:38,256 --> 00:01:41,688
ZARA: Time to take down Ryker and uncover the truth.
